'This is my Mummastory' 

I was in dream world when first time I saw my Daughter Auli. Today I will share the very important aspect of motherhood journey which is breastfeeding.
I had normal delivery but after delivery breastfeeding was very challenging .And my doctor advised me to breastfeed her as long as I can and why not it’s best nutrition for Auli. Also it will help my baby’s immune system and her growth . I was in complete pressure what to do. As she was not latching properly or sometime sore nipples or sometime I was so busy in work that my baby was hungry. 

After all mom hu so I found out the solution “ LuvLap adore electric breastpump” 
Which helps me to express milk easily and can store it . It follows baby’s natural suckling action too. Another thing it’s very  compact that even I can carry it every where. No matter if I am traveling , I can be rest assured my baby’s tummy is always full. So if you too are facing any issues regarding breastfeeding please use LuvLap adore electric breast pump .
